<head>
  <title>購入が完了しました - メルカリ スマホでかんたん フリマアプリ</title>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="single-container">
    <header class="single-header">
      <h1>
        <a href="/">
          <img src="//www-mercari-jp.akamaized.net/assets/img/common/common/logo.svg?1236411757" alt="mercari">
        </a>
      </h1>
    </header>
    <main class="single-main">
      <section class="l-single-container buy-item-container">
        <div class="transact-attention">
          <h3>
            <i class="fas fa-clock"></i>
            <span>発送をお待ちください</span>
          </h3>
          <p>出品者からの発送通知をお待ちください</p>
        </div>
        <h2 class="l-single-head">購入が完了しました</h2>
        <section class="buy-content buy-item">
          <div class="buy-content-inner">
            <h3 class="buy-item-image">
              <img data-src="<%= @product.product_images[0].image %>" class=" is-higher-height lazyloaded" alt="" src="<%= @product.product_images[0].image %>">
            </h3>
            <p class="buy-item-name bold"><%= @product.name %></p>
          </div>
        </section>
        <section class="buy-content buy-user-info buy-item">
          <div class="buy-content-inner">
            <p class="buy-price-ja bold">
              ¥ <%= price_delimiter(@product.price) %>
              <span class="item-shipping-fee f14 bold">送料込み</span>
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>
        <section class="buy-content buy-user-info">
          <div class="buy-content-inner">
            <h3>配送先 </h3>
            <address class="buy-user-info-text">
              〒<%= @buyer.address.postal_code %>
              <br>
              <%= @buyer.address.prefecture %>
              <%= @buyer.address.city %>
              <%= @buyer.address.street_number %>
              <%= @buyer.address.building_number %>
              <br>
              <%= @buyer.address.family_name %><%= @buyer.address.first_name %>
            </address>
          <p class="buy-user-info-text">
          </p>
        </div>
        </section>
        <section class="buy-content buy-done-flow">
          <h3>発送通知後の流れ</h3>
          <div>
            <i class="fas fa-laugh"></i>
            <i class="fas fa-meh"></i>
            <i class="fas fa-sad-tear"></i>
          </div>
          <p>商品を受け取ったら<br>出品者の評価をしましょう。<br>購入代金が出品者に振り込まれます。<br>評価後に取引は完了です。</p>
          <a href="<%= user_path(current_user.id) %>" class="bold">マイページへもどる</a>
        </section>
      </section>
    </main>
    <%= render partial: 'layouts/footer_simple' %>
  </div>
  <%= render partial: 'layouts/footer_scripts' %>
</body>
